{"TopicId":118422,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"UAV/Multi-Rotors/Drones anyone?","CreatedByName":"Astronut","CreatedById":2077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T00:42:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Astronut","CreatedById":2077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T00:42:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI recently took the plunge and bought myself a DJI Phantom 3. It\u0027s a fantastic piece of tech. Very easy to fly and takes great photos and video. Has anyone else here been bitten by the bug?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere are a few of the shots I have taken so far with it.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/RFZlh8G.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022RFZlh8G.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/w1PQAKk.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022w1PQAKk.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/rNdX3Fs.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022rNdX3Fs.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ZnSjXT5.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022ZnSjXT5.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/f4MENo2.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022f4MENo2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere is the Phantom itself:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ULEDqTF.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ULEDqTF.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eand the obligatory \u0027Dronie\u0027 \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ldFjfMX.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022ldFjfMX.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xtoro","CreatedById":79015,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T01:07:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI got an AR.Drone a few years ago, the one with 2 cameras. I played with it quite a bit for the first couple months. Haven\u0027t touched it since \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHows the battery runtime?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astronut","CreatedById":2077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T01:31:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMost of my flights are 15-18 minutes, but I make a point of landing with at least 20% battery left (the App squawks at you when you hit 30% by default). DJI claims 23 minutes of battery and I believe that, assuming you are willing to run it down below 10%.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T03:02:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u002B1 rep for the \u0027Dronie\u0027 ... first time I\u0027ve ever heard that one. lol\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"InterCity","CreatedById":98462,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T10:13:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Astronut\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Astronut\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eand the obligatory \u0027Dronie\u0027 \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENew term coined.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027m working on a drone that\u0027s flying itself atm, but can\u0027t make it to fly straight for more than 5 m. Its erratic flying is funny, but a failure nonetheless. Hope it gets better \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ChrisSpace","CreatedById":140622,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T11:07:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI need this.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astronut","CreatedById":2077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T15:18:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI can\u0027t claim the term \u0022Dronie\u0022 as it has been around for awhile now....\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dronie\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dronie\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EJebKerboom, that sounds like a great project. I was originally going to build my own but ended up taking the easy option by going with the Phantom 3. I would still like to build my own at some point though.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T15:28:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Astronut\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Astronut\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI can\u0027t claim the term \u0022Dronie\u0022 as it has been around for awhile now....\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dronie\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dronie\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E...\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou\u0027re still getting the rep for it. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flymetothemun","CreatedById":17689,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T15:40:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LordFerret\u0022 data-cite=\u0022LordFerret\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYou\u0027re still getting the rep for it. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI agree, just because the axe was invented millennia ago why shouldn\u0027t a firefighter get recognition for using one?\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}